Class Source

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.colorfulsoftware.atom.Source
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Source
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents an Atom 1.0 source element.
    Author:
    Bill Brown 
            atomSource =
          element atom:source {
          atomCommonAttributes,
          (atomAuthor*
          & atomCategory*
          & atomContributor*
          & atomGenerator?
          & atomIcon?
          & atomId?
          & atomLink*
          & atomLogo?
          & atomRights?
          & atomSubtitle?
          & atomTitle?
          & atomUpdated?
          & extensionElement*)
          }
    See Also:
    Atom Syndication Format, Serialized Form
